    "condition_number_kappa": 600,
    "condition_number_effective": 10,
    "regime": "Well-conditioned when saturation is avoided at some exposure for every pixel (dynamic-range cover). Degrades when (a) motion causes ghosting, (b) all exposures saturate in hotspots, (c) CRF calibration drifts. Under-covered bins (no exposure contains them unsaturated) are unrecoverable."
  },
  "C": {
    "solver_class": "Debevec-Malik weighted fusion + inverse CRF, Mertens exposure fusion, HDR-CNN / Kalantari-Ramamoorthi deep HDR, HDR-GAN",
